data.description: Fantastic opportunity to own a solid 5-bedroom, 1-bath Bryn Mawr twin at a price that allows you to make it your own!  Enter into the foyer and head to the light filled living room.  The dining room is generously sized and leads to the eat in kitchen with gas cooking.  There is also a laundry located on the first floor.  Heading up to the second level you will find 3 bedrooms and a bathroom with shower/tub combo.  The 3rd floor offers 2 additional bedrooms.  This home has an unfinished basement that provides lots of storage or could be finished off for added living space.  Fantastic location, close to train, shopping, and dining.  This home is being sold in “As-Is” condition and any contents remaining in the home at the time of closing will be the responsibility of the Buyer.  The U&O will also be the responsibility of the Buyer and must be indicated on the Agreement of Sale.
